4Geeks Academy offers a "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" course designed for beginners, allowing participants to launch careers as data scientists and build their first machine learning models within 16 weeks. Participants will learn programming languages and tools such as Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), and Streamlit while developing predictive models and tackling real-world data challenges. The course includes three weekly classes with a maximum of 12 students, culminating in a recognized certificate. The instruction is available in both English and Spanish. 

For more information, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning 

